title: Need an upgrade!
text:
Oh this place remind me home (this is what i was thinking when i bit the pizza fritta - a traditional fried pizza from napoli).
But unfortunately isn't just that on the menu.. like the arancini, unsalted and bland, ore the crocchette, same reason..
Or when we ordered some pizzas and they give us different (we deal with the waiter and tell him was fine, cause we was hungry ahahah) ... but as i say, that bit of pizza was legendary, we will come back for super and hopefully the things are getting better, cause it's a new opening and we understand.

title: Oooh that curry!
text: A surprising lunch in this place a few days ago! We had 2 different curry for have a look of the menu and the quality.. well, let's say those chef know there job!! One of the best in newtown!!

title: Best Pad thai
text:
Been here with my girlfriend few days ago.
Such a long time a don't a pad thai like this.. complete and full of flavour.. happy and for sure i will come back.

title: Crispy and good
text:
A good meal deal between beers and chicken in different flavour. For sure this place make happy a lot of mates group!
Anyway, nice tasting of the bites, sweety or spicy.. good meal deal in the area

title: A nice break
text:
Been here with my mate few days ago, service 8/10, smiling faces and happy place (cause of the beers maybe).
The food 8/10 dumplings and takoyaki balls really internet flavours.
And of course the amount of different beers it's a good point.
We really enjoyed
place: Harajuku Gyoza Beer Stadium Darling Harbour

title: Love it!!
text: Such a lovely yummy tasting of the dishes!! Literally everything was really good..unsatisfied only about the service and the waitress, make us a bit uncomfortable, maybe cause of the language or, well, wherever.. the kitchen doing really well!

title: Miss something, like the love in the plate
text:
We been here for a good sweety fatty breakfast and we left really disappointed...
Let's say, tge service was 10/10, the waitress was really kind and professional, the order come true as we ask, but..
We order 2 different pancakes to have a look and try, but in the end was just chocolate topping and some fruit, the pancakes wasn't tasting good, missing flavour for sure.. luckily the smoothies we had, save hour morning

title: Best dumpling ever!!
text: In the chinatown heart, close to the cbd of sydney, there is this small place, with a classic Chinese menu, but the tasting of the dishes ita literally yummy!!

title: Ding Dong all night!
text:
The title mean abot the bell the chef smash all night and unfortunately all the customers outside hear for all night!

But forget about that, infact i give 4/5
- for the service first, because the waiters was super gentil and professional and make our dinner comfortable!
- and for the food second, tuna tartare nice, sweet and soft, but miss some flavour like mint and lime for example.
And the linguine Vongole, sweet and tasting (but, if was me, chef, try the emulsion before to add the pasta otherwise the linguine are super oily) (im an italian chef so i know what im talking about when i recognize the old school plate).. but in the end without this small details, the place and the service deserve!

title: Tasty Lobster
text: First time we been here, located behind covent garden, you can try a nice butter lobster o different meat offer like pork or burger. Famous for the fried shrimps on Tuesday! Not to high price! Nice for what u eat

title: A lovely dinner
text: Located in soho, this small but comfortable restaurant serve one of the best bao in London, tasty and delicious in different feeling like pork, chicken and veg. Apparently it's a company with different point like in borough or tottenham rd..

title: A good italian place!
text: Located in soho, the cecconi's it's part of a big company of restaurants located in london. Offer a nice service and a good tasting italian food! Like burrata and tagliatelle bolognese!

title: The best ramen!
text: Located close to the Tottenham court rd station (central/northern line) we had a lovely dinner, japanese tasting with a nice service and a wonderful food! All the ramen bowl are good! And a good qualiti of the starter and drink!

title: Greek styke Dinner
text: Located in soho, this restaurant offer a nice greek food dinner, but with something extra, a new tasting, a different way to cook greek! I like it! Lovely waitress! 10 point for her haha

title: A nice dinner
text: Located in china town, close to the piccadilly circus station, i had one of my best vietnamese food tasting! Meal with fresh and good ingredients! Lovely staff and place! Good location!

title: My favourite breakfast in town
text: Located in holborn station on the piccadilly/central line (blue and red), this lovely breakfast restaurant make one of the best food in the area!! We talking about pancakes, omelet, smoothies, juice and coffe!!! Definitely u need to try!!!

title: Such a good Pizza
text: Princi, a fresh italian restaurant located nearly to soho and china town, with a nice and tasty product like the nice napolitan pizza and the good bakery section! It's a really busy restaurant but the staff doi g really well, kitchen and service!!

title: Best Pierogi in town
text: in christmas time the best you can do is enjoy the pierogi every day, and this one it's the best shop to doing! a lot of different flavour, all of them super tasty and nice
